channel.title: Ancient Aliens
channel.description:
So, has anyone seen the new series on the History channel called Ancient Aliens? I saw an episode today. If it were possible to create a continuous facepalm, I would have been doing it. Unfortunately I had to settle for a repeating facepalm. Where to begin? Okay, first off, apparently ancient civilizations flew around in boxes and landed on ancient runways. They wrapped a special paper around massive building blocks to make them hover. And oh yeah, Ezekiel (The bible Ezekiel) apparently built a hangar for a space ship and was told to do so by beings in shiny metal armor who came from the sky.
All of this is presented as if it were emerging factual theories, with no counter-arguments involved. And we wonder why increasingly unintelligent people come about every day?
No really. DVR it if you have to. It's entertaining JUST to see how ridiculous this show really gets.
